title.rendered: BOSS AIR DIGITAL DUAL LED GAUGE

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR DIGITAL DUAL LED GAUGE

Boss Air Digital Dual LED Gauge available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Features:

  • 0-220psi
  • Blue LED Dual Display
  • 52mm mounting
  • Twin sensors with 1/8″ NPT thread
  • Curved Sun bezel
  • Auto Light Dim Function

Extra options include:

  • Gauge Kit
    • Dual needle gauge 200psi with fittings and 10mtrs of Airline
  • 1/4″ Airline Fittings Kit
    • 1/4″ Airline valve fitting kit sealant-less
  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
